---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Lance Owide"
  description="Lance Owide is General Manager B2B at BigCommerce, focused on the future of B2B commerce and AI."
>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <aside class="about-aside">
        <img src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Lance Owide" class="about-photo" />
        <div class="about-meta">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Role</span>
            <span class="meta-value">General Manager B2B</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Company</span>
            <a href="https://www.bigcommerce.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="meta-link">BigCommerce</a>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">LinkedIn</span>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lance-owide/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="meta-link">lance-owide</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="page-label">About</div>
        <h1 class="page-title">Lance Owide</h1>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            I'm the General Manager of B2B at BigCommerce, where I lead the global strategy for B2B commerce — spanning go-to-market, sales, customer success, and product direction. My focus is on helping manufacturers, distributors, and wholesalers build best-in-class digital buying experiences for their business customers.
          </p>
          <p>
            B2B commerce is in the middle of a massive transformation. Buyers increasingly expect consumer-grade digital experiences, and AI is accelerating what's possible — from intelligent product discovery and personalised pricing to automated procurement workflows. This sits at the intersection of what I think about most.
          </p>
          <p>
            Outside of BigCommerce, I spend time exploring how AI is changing the way we build products and companies. I'm particularly interested in applied AI — how large language models and agents can be put to work on real business problems today, not just in theory.
          </p>
          <p>
            I'm also a mentor on MentorCruise, working with founders and operators on business strategy and go-to-market.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="currently">
          <h2 class="currently-title">Currently</h2>
          <ul class="currently-list">
            <li>Building the B2B product and GTM strategy at BigCommerce</li>
            <li>Exploring AI applications in commerce and B2B workflows</li>
            <li>Mentoring operators and founders on strategy and growth</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-aside {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 2rem);
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1rem;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-subtle);
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .meta-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .meta-link:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .about-content .page-label {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-content .page-title {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .prose {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .currently {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .currently-title {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .currently-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .currently-list li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .currently-list li::before {
    content: '→';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-aside {
      position: static;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .about-photo {
      width: 100px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
